## 최근 변경

```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  file.link as "페이지",
  date as "날짜",
  status as "상태",
  scope as "범위"
FROM "{{WIKI_ROOT}}"
WHERE file.name != "index" AND file.name != "log"
SORT date DESC
LIMIT 8
```

